    description: "The Discipleship Pastor will shepherd our church family through the leading of our life groups, adult ministries, developing serve opportunities both locally and globally, and connecting with people who are new to our church.\n\nFCC is a multi-generational, non-denominational church celebrating our 100th year in 2024. Located in the Milwaukee, WI to Chicago, IL corridor, the church serves the community with weekly worship services, a strong kids and teens ministry, and a volunteer run foster-family assistance program. We meet in a 55,000 sq ft facility built less than 25 years ago which is debt free. FCC is a place for EVERY.ONE. and is guided by our mission statement to meet people where they are and help the take their next steps toward Jesus. Current staff include a full time Lead Pastor, Worship Pastor, Discipleship Pastor (retiring) and Executive Director who oversees staff and financials, all led by a four person elder board. Visit: kenoshafcc.com for additional details about who we are.",
